name: YOUTH MASK
description:
MÁSCARAS #1 YOUTH MASK 

The work ''YOUTH MASK'' is the first mask, of four, in the MÁSCARAS collection, developed by OGU, oburaco and ZALA.

This piece visualy solidify the youth existence, from the teenager development to an adult life, constantly changing.

3D modeling by OBU and oburaco.
Analog textures developed by ZALA, with spray NOU and acrylic on paper.
